# CODE OWNERS CONFIGURATION
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Project: Supernova - Audio Visualizer + AI Themes
# Purpose: Automatic code review assignment and ownership definition
# Documentation: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# This file defines individuals or teams responsible for reviewing and
# approving changes to specific files or directories in the repository.
#
# IMPORTANT NOTES:
# - Code owners are automatically requested for review when PRs modify their files
# - At least one code owner approval is required before merging (if branch protection is enabled)
# - Order matters: Last matching pattern takes precedence
# - Use team mentions (@org/team) for better scalability in organizations
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

